    "title": "Study shows how toxic RFK Jr.’s change to measles vaccine is for US toddlers",
    "text": "A new study shows RFK Jr.'s decision to remove the measles vaccine recommendation is dangerous for US toddlers. The advisory group did not consider how removing the vaccine would affect children, and did not use the proper evidence-based rules. As a result, private insurance companies no longer have to pay the cost of the shot, and a federal program that delivers vaccines to about half of US children, especially those in poor families, can no longer use it. Researchers found the decision is very dangerous for young children.",
